Package edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user

Class Faculty

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user.User
edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user.Faculty
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Faculty>
public class Faculty extends User implements Comparable<Faculty>
Student class contains the first name, last name, id, email, password, and maximum credits for the student to enter in their directory while creating their directory. A Student will be listed in the directory after they add the student to it.
Author:
